<style>
    .mybox { width: 50%; height: 50px;
             float: left;
             margin-top: 2px; padding: 8px;
             border-width: 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: #c1bbbb; 
             background-color: #ffd800; }
    .mybox1 { box-sizing: border-box; background-clip: border-box; }
    .mybox2 { box-sizing: border-box; background-clip: border-box; }
    .mybox3 { box-sizing: content-box; background-clip: content-box; }
    .mybox4 { box-sizing: content-box; background-clip: content-box; }
    .mybox5 { display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;
              padding: 10px; margin: 5px;
              border: 10px solid red; /*边框宽度、边框样式、边框颜色*/
              background-color: Blue; color: White; text-align: left; }
</style>
<div class="row" style="border:5px ridge red">
    <div class="col-md-6" style="border-right:5px ridge blue">
        <h5>box-sizing:盒大小（宽度都是50%，高度都是50px）</h5>
        <div class="mybox mybox1">border-box1</div>
        <div class="mybox mybox2">border-box2</div>
        <div class="mybox mybox3">content-box1</div>
        <div class="mybox mybox4">content-box2</div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h5>content、padding、border、margin基本用法</h5>
        <div class="text-center">
            <div class="mybox5" style="width: 40%; height: 80px;">
                mybox5
            </div>
            <p>
                今天天气很好，阳光明媚，没有雾霾。<br />
                a1<span class="mybox5" style="width: 60px; height: 50px;">span1</span>
                a2<span class="mybox5" style="width: 60px; height: 50px;">span2</span>
                a3
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
